1
00:00:19,649 --> 00:00:22,908
-我們今晚會抓到浣熊嗎，爸爸？    -最好是
{\fs12}-Think we'll get a coon tonight, Daddy?  -We'd better.{\r}

2
00:00:25,556 --> 00:00:28,926
耶穌，你會降臨這裡嗎？
{\fs12}Jesus, will you come by here?{\r}

3
00:00:29,046 --> 00:00:32,667
哦，耶穌，你會降臨這裡嗎？
{\fs12}Oh, Jesus, will you come by here?{\r}

4
00:00:33,308 --> 00:00:37,931
耶穌，你會降臨這裡嗎？
{\fs12}Jesus, will you come by here?{\r}

5
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:42,722
現在是非常時期...
{\fs12}Now is a needy time...{\r}

6
00:00:42,842 --> 00:00:46,446
哦，現在是非常時期...
{\fs12}Oh, now is a needy time...{\r}

7
00:00:46,969 --> 00:00:51,130
現在是非常時期
{\fs12}Now is a needy time.{\r}

8
00:00:54,962 --> 00:00:57,980
來吧，如果你不能久留...
{\fs12}Come, if you don't stay long...{\r}

9
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:01,576
哦，來吧，如果你不能久留...
{\fs12}Oh, come, if you don't stay long...{\r}

10
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:06,066
來吧，來吧，如果你不能久留
{\fs12}Come, if you don't stay long.{\r}

11
00:01:08,092 --> 00:01:10,900
現在是非常時期
{\fs12}Now is a needy time...{\r}

12
00:01:11,020 --> 00:01:14,474
哦，現在是非常時期...
{\fs12}Oh, now is a needy time...{\r}

13
00:01:14,594 --> 00:01:19,229
耶穌，你不會降臨這裡嗎？
{\fs12}Jesus, won't you come by here?{\r}

14
00:01:20,836 --> 00:01:23,651
他抓到一個了！快，男孩，我們走吧
{\fs12}He's got one already! Come on, boy, let's go.{\r}

15
00:01:28,713 --> 00:01:30,713
我聽到你了，男孩，快！
{\fs12}I hear you, boy, come on!{\r}

16
00:01:49,807 --> 00:01:52,252
給我那盞燈，男孩，快，讓我們...
{\fs12}Give me that lamp, boy, come on, let's...{\r}

17
00:01:52,372 --> 00:01:53,141
天
{\fs12}Man.{\r}

18
00:01:57,141 --> 00:01:59,659
有了。現在快，男孩，我們走吧！
{\fs12}There it is. Now come on, boy, let's go!{\r}

19
00:02:03,807 --> 00:02:06,030
去吧，桑德！我聽到你了，快！
{\fs12}Go, Sounder! I hear you. Come on!{\r}

20
00:02:25,688 --> 00:02:30,503
他應該在樹叢裡抓到他了。老浣熊你完蛋了！
{\fs12}I think he's got him treed, boy. It's all over now for you, old coon!{\r}

21
00:02:31,836 --> 00:02:33,984
他在那。快，我們走
{\fs12}There he is. Come on, let's go.{\r}

22
00:02:44,969 --> 00:02:48,450
桌上甜美的肉。我們聽到了，男孩。快！
{\fs12}Sweet meat on the table. We hear you, boy. Come on!{\r}

23
00:03:00,006 --> 00:03:01,043
射擊！
{\fs12}Shoot!{\r}

24
00:03:03,783 --> 00:03:04,746
該死的
{\fs12}Damn.{\r}

25
00:03:19,469 --> 00:03:22,432
哦，桑德，現在別放棄。快，男孩！
{\fs12}Oh, Sounder, don't give up now. Come on, boy!{\r}

26
00:03:26,728 --> 00:03:30,209
那隻狗已經找到了。快，小子，我們走
{\fs12}That dog done found one already. Come on, sonny, let's go.{\r}

27
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,257
桑德！
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

28
00:03:52,109 --> 00:03:53,146
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

29
00:03:56,701 --> 00:03:57,886
哇，開槍！
{\fs12}Aww, shoot!{\r}

30
00:04:10,701 --> 00:04:13,812
快，桑德，現在別放棄。快，男孩！
{\fs12}Come on, Sounder, don't give up now. Come on, boy!{\r}

31
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,317
該死！
{\fs12}Dammit!{\r}

32
00:04:55,984 --> 00:05:00,428
以前一隻公牛都無法阻止那條狗抓到那隻浣熊
{\fs12}I remember a time when a bull couldn't stop that dog from catching that coon.{\r}

33
00:05:32,112 --> 00:05:33,594
沒關係，兒子
{\fs12}It's alright, son.{\r}

34
00:05:34,853 --> 00:05:36,881
老桑德完成了他的工作
{\fs12}Old Sounder did his job.{\r}

35
00:05:37,001 --> 00:05:41,964
只是，當我想到餐桌上沒有肉時，我就...
{\fs12}It's just, when I realized there wasn't gonna be no meat on the table, I just...{\r}

36
00:05:42,084 --> 00:05:44,038
...一時表現得很愚蠢
{\fs12}...acted foolish for a minute.{\r}

37
00:05:45,297 --> 00:05:49,354
如果要怪人，就怪我吧，因為第一槍就該打中他
{\fs12}If anybody's to blame, it's me, 'cause I oughta nailed him on that first shot.{\r}

38
00:05:49,474 --> 00:05:51,075
太暗了，爸爸
{\fs12}It's too dark, Daddy.{\r}

39
00:05:54,670 --> 00:05:55,682
是啊
{\fs12}Yeah.{\r}

40
00:05:57,831 --> 00:05:59,115
好吧...
{\fs12}Alright, well...{\r}

41
00:06:01,819 --> 00:06:05,276
我們最好還是回木屋，桑德！
{\fs12}Well, I guess we better get on back to the cabin. Sounder!{\r}

42
00:06:18,087 --> 00:06:22,112
你知道，兒子：沒有其他狗可以跟得上桑德
{\fs12}You know, son: there ain't no dog as good as Sounder.{\r}

43
00:06:22,964 --> 00:06:27,483
多年來，我們一直在樹林追逐浣熊和負鼠...
{\fs12}In all the years we've been tracking coons and possums in these woods...{\r}

44
00:06:27,976 --> 00:06:32,223
他連一個都沒撕裂過他們。嗯，沒有...
{\fs12}He ain't never tore one of them up yet. Mm-mmm, no...{\r}

45
00:06:32,343 --> 00:06:35,340
他們被他抓回來時，還是活繃亂跳的
{\fs12}He always brought them back whole and healthy.{\r}

46
00:06:35,867 --> 00:06:36,855
現在你明白了嗎？
{\fs12}Now you see?{\r}

47
00:06:36,975 --> 00:06:41,413
這就是好狗和又兇又髒的獵犬之間的差別...
{\fs12}Now that's the difference between a hound dog that's mean and dirty...{\r}

48
00:06:41,533 --> 00:06:45,315
...像老桑德就是一條很棒的狗
{\fs12}...to one that's great. Like old Sounder here.{\r}

49
00:07:03,739 --> 00:07:06,165
我們把一隻困住了，卻被他放走了
{\fs12}We had one cornered, but he got away.{\r}

50
00:07:29,423 --> 00:07:33,300
-你一定累了，小男孩。是吧，大衛李？  -是的，先生。
{\fs12}-I bet you you're tired, little boy. Ain't you, David Lee? -Yes, sir.{\r}

51
00:07:40,642 --> 00:07:42,553
你應該也累了，桑德...
{\fs12}You ought to be tired, too, Sounder...{\r}

52
00:07:42,673 --> 00:07:46,278
...因為浣熊今晚肯定把你操壞了
{\fs12}...cause that coon sure whipped the hell out of you tonight.{\r}

53
00:07:46,398 --> 00:07:49,833
浣熊也打敗了你，爸爸，你還有一枝大獵槍呢
{\fs12}He beat you too, Daddy, and you had a big shootin' rifle.{\r}

54
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:53,665
男孩，不要和你老爸開這種玩笑
{\fs12}You don't make funny with your daddy like that, boy.{\r}

55
00:07:56,233 --> 00:07:58,406
-大衛李          -是的，先生？
{\fs12}-David Lee.      -Yes, sir?{\r}

56
00:08:01,208 --> 00:08:04,368
你今晚夠累了，所以，呃...
{\fs12}You had a rough time out there tonight, so, uh...{\r}

57
00:08:04,813 --> 00:08:07,302
明天就別去學校了
{\fs12}...you stay home from that school tomorrow.{\r}

58
00:08:07,422 --> 00:08:08,932
但我想去
{\fs12}But I want to go.{\r}

59
00:08:09,648 --> 00:08:12,932
-你在學校有學到東西嗎？     -有，先生
{\fs12}-Are you learning anything at that school?    -Yes, sir.{\r}

60
00:08:20,902 --> 00:08:25,865
夜晚到了這個時刻，月亮跑的像一隻受驚嚇的兔子
{\fs12}When the night comes in these parts, that old moon runs like a scared rabbit.{\r}

61
00:08:27,095 --> 00:08:32,675
你整晚待在這裡，會看不到四周的東西
{\fs12}You can stay here all night just looking and not see a thing out yonder.{\r}

62
00:08:34,063 --> 00:08:36,433
爸爸，我們明天再打獵嗎？
{\fs12}Are we going hunting again tomorrow, Daddy?{\r}

63
00:08:36,553 --> 00:08:37,742
哦耶
{\fs12}Oh, yeah.{\r}

64
00:08:42,083 --> 00:08:46,355
你很納悶，是嗎？怎麼運氣那麼背
{\fs12}I guess you wonder why, though, huh? What with the luck we've been having.{\r}

65
00:08:46,475 --> 00:08:48,503
但是，就像我常說的...
{\fs12}But, like I always say...{\r}

66
00:08:48,623 --> 00:08:51,364
“你有些時後會得不到你想追求的...”
{\fs12}"You lose some of the time what you always go after..."{\r}

67
00:08:51,484 --> 00:08:54,003
“...但你不去追求時，什麼都別想得到”
{\fs12}"...but you lose all the time what you don't go after."{\r}

68
00:08:54,123 --> 00:08:57,114
現在，誰說我沒給你做個好榜樣呢，男孩？
{\fs12}Now, who says I didn't put my mark on you, boy?{\r}

69
00:08:59,172 --> 00:09:00,703
大衛李？
{\fs12}David Lee?{\r}

70
00:09:01,098 --> 00:09:03,098
兒子，該去睡覺了
{\fs12}Time to get to bed, son.{\r}

71
00:09:03,218 --> 00:09:04,678
晚安，爸爸
{\fs12}Goodnight, Daddy.{\r}

72
00:09:05,147 --> 00:09:06,629
晚安，兒子
{\fs12}Goodnight, son.{\r}

73
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:17,151
別吵醒喬西梅和厄爾
{\fs12}Don't wake Josie Mae and Earl, now.{\r}

74
00:09:17,878 --> 00:09:21,927
你也該去睡覺了，獵犬。去吧，下去那裡。去！
{\fs12}It's your bedtime too, hound dog. Now go on, get under there. Go on!{\r}

75
00:09:33,625 --> 00:09:36,119
你一定想喝一杯熱咖啡
{\fs12}I bet you could use a hot cup of coffee.{\r}

76
00:09:39,892 --> 00:09:43,053
當然囉，麗貝卡小姐...嗯
{\fs12}I sure could, Miss Rebecca...mmm.{\r}

77
00:09:43,522 --> 00:09:45,497
哦，納森李...
{\fs12}Oh, Nathan Lee...{\r}

78
00:09:50,385 --> 00:09:53,595
該死！那男孩吃光我的核桃
{\fs12}Dammit! That boy done bitten my walnuts.{\r}

79
00:09:53,715 --> 00:09:57,545
我撿了2磅，撿到手指破皮見骨，賣到小貨鋪...幾乎沒有價值...

{\fs12}I skin my fingers to the bone to pick 2 pounds that's worth almost nothing...{\r}

80
00:09:57,665 --> 00:10:00,239
...也得不到幾個錢，他卻吃掉快一半
{\fs12}...at the commissary, and he done took about half of it.{\r}

81
00:10:00,359 --> 00:10:02,462
麗貝卡，男孩餓了嘛
{\fs12}The boy is hungry, Rebecca.{\r}

82
00:10:11,651 --> 00:10:15,059
我們以前經歷過這種艱困時期，納森李 ...
{\fs12}We've been through these hard times before, Nathan Lee...{\r}

83
00:10:15,179 --> 00:10:16,590
...我們撐過來了
{\fs12}...and we made it.{\r}

84
00:10:16,710 --> 00:10:19,084
麗貝卡，我們撐過了什麼？
{\fs12}And what did we make it to, Rebecca?{\r}

85
00:10:19,204 --> 00:10:22,206
在另一季給帕金斯老頭繳田租？
{\fs12}Another season sharecropping for old man Perkins?{\r}

86
00:10:22,326 --> 00:10:23,792
努力工作到死...
{\fs12}Working ourselves to death...{\r}

87
00:10:23,912 --> 00:10:28,205
...讓他變得更有錢，收成時我們甚至連吃的都沒有？
{\fs12}...so he can get richer, and we can't even eat when cropping time is done?{\r}

88
00:10:49,363 --> 00:10:50,523
納森...
{\fs12}Nathan...{\r}

89
00:11:50,330 --> 00:11:51,344
{\fs12}Nathan?{\r}

90
00:12:02,668 --> 00:12:03,648
{\fs12}Nathan?{\r}

91
00:12:16,257 --> 00:12:17,289
{\fs12}Nathan?{\r}

92
00:12:20,508 --> 00:12:21,557
{\fs12}Nathan?{\r}

93
00:13:31,494 --> 00:13:35,132
快，你們全部都起床吧！廚房裡煮著肉呢
{\fs12}Come on, y'all, get up! There's meat cooking in the kitchen.{\r}

94
00:13:35,594 --> 00:13:37,589
快，起床了！快
{\fs12}Come on, get up! Come on.{\r}

95
00:13:49,370 --> 00:13:51,767
-爸爸，裡面有什麼？     -香腸和肉骨
{\fs12}-What's in there, Daddy?   -Sausage and ham bone.{\r}

96
00:13:51,887 --> 00:13:53,141
別那樣做！
{\fs12}Don't do that!{\r}

97
00:13:53,261 --> 00:13:55,295
這從哪裡來的？
{\fs12}Where did it come from?{\r}

98
00:13:56,432 --> 00:13:58,496
 -早安，媽媽     -早安
{\fs12}-Morning, Mama.    -Morning.{\r}

99
00:13:58,616 --> 00:14:00,451
爐子上有肉在煮
{\fs12}There's meat cooking on the stove.{\r}

100
00:14:00,571 --> 00:14:02,813
沒錯，去洗臉
{\fs12}That's right. Go wash up.{\r}

101
00:14:03,162 --> 00:14:06,243
-哪裡來的？      -有肉的地方
{\fs12}-Where'd it come from?   -Where all meat comes from.{\r}

102
00:14:06,363 --> 00:14:11,196
去洗臉，動作快點。去學校還要走6英里
{\fs12}Now go wash up & be snappy about it. You got 6 miles ahead of you to that school.{\r}

103
00:14:22,613 --> 00:14:24,064
早安，納森
{\fs12}Morning, Nathan.{\r}

104
00:14:24,537 --> 00:14:25,569
早安
{\fs12}Morning.{\r}

105
00:14:26,584 --> 00:14:28,508
你吃了嗎？
{\fs12}Did you have any to eat?{\r}

106
00:14:28,628 --> 00:14:32,374
哦，不，讓孩子們先吃。麗貝卡...
{\fs12}Oh, no, I'll wait until after the children. Rebecca...{\r}

107
00:14:32,636 --> 00:14:33,703
什麼事？
{\fs12}Yes?{\r}

108
00:14:36,195 --> 00:14:38,364
外面的天氣怎麼樣？
{\fs12}What's the weather like out there?{\r}

109
00:14:39,501 --> 00:14:40,673
很熱
{\fs12}It's hot.{\r}

110
00:14:41,426 --> 00:14:45,012
那麼，是我們今天棒球比賽的好天氣囉？
{\fs12}Gonna be good baseball weather for our game today, then, huh?{\r}

111
00:14:45,132 --> 00:14:46,122
嗯-嗯
{\fs12}Mm-hmm.{\r}

112
00:14:48,946 --> 00:14:49,935
早安，爸爸
{\fs12}Morning, Daddy.{\r}

113
00:14:50,055 --> 00:14:51,920
你也早安！
{\fs12}Well...morning back at you!{\r}

114
00:14:52,414 --> 00:14:55,253
嘿，你給我留下了一些，是嗎？
{\fs12}Hey, now, you save some of that for me, huh?{\r}

115
00:14:56,017 --> 00:14:57,054
桑德？
{\fs12}Sounder?{\r}

116
00:14:57,597 --> 00:14:59,227
嘿，桑德！來吧
{\fs12}Hey, Sounder! Come on.{\r}

117
00:15:00,585 --> 00:15:05,054
給你，男孩。你今晚應該有好表現了吧？
{\fs12}There you go, boy. Now that ought to put you in good shape for tonight, huh?{\r}

118
00:15:08,674 --> 00:15:10,970
大衛李，不要一整個早上都賴在餐桌子
{\fs12}Now don't take all morning at that table, David Lee.{\r}

119
00:15:11,090 --> 00:15:13,933
媽媽，我和厄爾什麼時候和大衛李一起上學？
{\fs12}Mama, when can me and Earl go to school with David Lee?{\r}

120
00:15:14,053 --> 00:15:15,217
也許很快
{\fs12}Maybe soon.{\r}

121
00:15:46,388 --> 00:15:49,224
告訴你我們有一樣東西很多，那就是木頭
{\fs12}Tell you one thing we got plenty of, is wood.{\r}

122
00:15:54,297 --> 00:15:55,889
我要去了，媽媽
{\fs12}Ready to go, Mama.{\r}

123
00:15:56,396 --> 00:15:58,670
把襯衫塞進去，大衛李
{\fs12}Well, tuck that shirt in, David Lee.{\r}

124
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:01,910
你放學校後，要立刻回家，聽到了嗎？
{\fs12}And when you get out of that school, you come straight on home, you hear?{\r}

125
00:16:02,173 --> 00:16:05,059
你得把我洗好的衣服，拿回去給為柏瑞特女士
{\fs12}You're gonna have to take this laundry work I've done for Ms. Boatwright.{\r}

126
00:16:05,179 --> 00:16:06,196
日安
{\fs12}Good day.{\r}

127
00:16:09,328 --> 00:16:10,360
再見，爸爸
{\fs12}Bye, Daddy.{\r}

128
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,445
再見，兒子
{\fs12}Bye, son.{\r}

129
00:16:17,987 --> 00:16:20,541
你昨晚去了哪兒，納森？
{\fs12}Where was it you went last night, Nathan?{\r}

130
00:16:21,251 --> 00:16:23,368
麗貝卡，我去做該做的事
{\fs12}I did what I had to do, Rebecca.{\r}

131
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:17,385
...四海皆兄弟！
{\fs12}...and crown thy good with brotherhood, from sea to shining sea!{\r}

132
00:17:38,325 --> 00:17:40,809
《頑童歷險記》第34章
{\fs12}Huckleberry Finn, Chapter 34.{\r}

133
00:17:41,507 --> 00:17:43,711
-對不起，克萊女士           -你遲到了
{\fs12}-I'm sorry, Ms. Clay. -You're late.{\r}

134
00:17:43,831 --> 00:17:46,247
-是的，女士         -那就坐下吧
{\fs12}-Yes, ma'am. -Well, take your seat.{\r}

135
00:17:48,256 --> 00:17:50,968
被打斷之前，我們講到哪裡了？
{\fs12}Now where were we, before we were interrupted?{\r}

136
00:17:51,088 --> 00:17:55,396
噢，是的。《頑童歷險記》第34章    [註：刪節本] 
{\fs12}Oh, yeah. Huckleberry Finn, Chapter 34. [NB: her edition is abridged/censored.]{\r}

137
00:17:55,516 --> 00:17:58,367
這一章叫做“我們為吉姆打氣”
{\fs12}This chapter is called, "We Cheer Up Jim."{\r}

138
00:17:58,729 --> 00:17:59,954
開始了：
{\fs12}Here we go:{\r}

139
00:18:00,305 --> 00:18:04,171
湯姆說：“這給誰吃呀？餵狗嗎？”
{\fs12}Tom says: "What's the vittles for? Going to feed the dogs?"{\r}

140
