煮一些玉米糊給你們大家吃
{\fs12}And fix some of that corn mush for y'all to eat.{\r}

276
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:58,558
要找桑德，別跑得太遠
{\fs12}Don't go too far now looking for Sounder.{\r}

277
00:28:58,678 --> 00:29:02,598
有陌生人問你問題，什麼都別說，聽到嗎？
{\fs12}Anybody comes that's a stranger asking you questions, don't say nothing, hear?{\r}

278
00:29:02,718 --> 00:29:03,974
我不會
{\fs12}I won't.{\r}

279
00:29:04,094 --> 00:29:05,843
-再見，兒子       -再見，媽媽
{\fs12}-Bye, son. -Bye, Mama.{\r}

280
00:29:05,963 --> 00:29:07,873
我不會去太久
{\fs12}I won't be gone too long.{\r}

281
00:29:19,130 --> 00:29:21,099
-再見，媽媽     -再見，媽媽
{\fs12}-Bye, Mama.     -Bye, Mama.{\r}

282
00:31:28,704 --> 00:31:29,951
你好嗎？
{\fs12}How do you do?{\r}

283
00:31:30,393 --> 00:31:32,282
麗貝卡，早安
{\fs12}Good morning, Rebecca.{\r}

284
00:31:32,402 --> 00:31:35,378
今天早上我在等你來
{\fs12}I was sort of expecting you this morning.{\r}

285
00:31:35,692 --> 00:31:37,662
我來看看納森
{\fs12}I've come to see Nathan.{\r}

286
00:31:38,044 --> 00:31:39,250
呃...
{\fs12}Well...{\r}

287
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:41,682
我很想，但我不能
{\fs12}I wish I could, but I can't let you.{\r}

288
00:31:43,531 --> 00:31:45,840
我不明白，楊警長
{\fs12}I don't understand that, Sheriff Young.{\r}

289
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,448
這很簡單
{\fs12}Well, it's simple.{\r}

290
00:31:48,634 --> 00:31:50,382
這是規定
{\fs12}That's the rules.{\r}

291
00:31:50,502 --> 00:31:51,804
我只能遵守
{\fs12}I follow them.{\r}

292
00:31:51,924 --> 00:31:54,678
除了周日和節假日外，不准會客
{\fs12}Ain't no visiting, except Sunday and holidays.{\r}

293
00:31:54,798 --> 00:31:56,266
婦女同胞則一律禁見
{\fs12}No womenfolk no time.{\r}

294
00:31:56,386 --> 00:31:59,182
你是在告訴我，我不能見自己的丈夫？
{\fs12}You mean to tell me, I can't see my own husband?{\r}

295
00:31:59,302 --> 00:32:02,691
在蘭斯敦 是這樣規定的...
{\fs12}Well, that's the way they do things here in Lansdowne...{\r}

296
00:32:03,133 --> 00:32:04,862
我只是奉命行事
{\fs12}I just follow orders.{\r}

297
00:32:08,608 --> 00:32:12,809
但是...我得見他，警長先生，我必須看到納森
{\fs12}But...I've got to see him, Mr. Sheriff, you know, I've got to see Nathan.{\r}

298
00:32:13,653 --> 00:32:15,882
我想幫你...
{\fs12}Well, I'd like to help you...{\r}

299
00:32:16,002 --> 00:32:19,556
...除了讓我們兩為難，並無濟於事
{\fs12}...but that wouldn't do anything but get us both in trouble.{\r}

300
00:32:24,579 --> 00:32:26,468
他們會給他一個審判？
{\fs12}They gonna give him a trial?{\r}

301
00:32:26,588 --> 00:32:28,659
可能在下週某些時候
{\fs12}Probably some time next week.{\r}

302
00:32:29,463 --> 00:32:31,284
我要告訴你 我會怎麼做...
{\fs12}I'll tell you what I'll do...{\r}

303
00:32:31,404 --> 00:32:36,479
只要我知道是哪一天，我就會開車去你家通知你
{\fs12}Soon as I find out what day, I'll drive on out to your place and let you know.{\r}

304
00:32:45,136 --> 00:32:46,342
麗貝卡
{\fs12}Rebecca.{\r}

305
00:32:53,788 --> 00:32:56,501
警長先生，你找到了一份低賤的工作
{\fs12}You've got you a low-life job, Mr. Sheriff.{\r}

306
00:33:32,355 --> 00:33:34,526
麗貝卡，我正想找你
{\fs12}Rebecca, you're just the one I want to see.{\r}

307
00:33:34,646 --> 00:33:37,260
我帶這些核桃來交易
{\fs12}I brought these walnuts to trade.{\r}

308
00:33:42,658 --> 00:33:44,487
這是1元2美分
{\fs12}That's 1 dollar and 20 cents.{\r}

309
00:33:44,607 --> 00:33:47,181
-我想拿我要的東西   -希望不是太多，因為...
{\fs12}-I want to get me some things.   -I hope it ain't a lot, because...{\r}

310
00:33:47,301 --> 00:33:49,914
...在耕作時期之前，不能再讓你賒帳了
{\fs12}...I can't give you no more credit until cropping season gets back.{\r}

311
00:33:50,034 --> 00:33:51,690
也就是說，如果納森趕得上的話
{\fs12}That is, if Nathan makes it.{\r}

312
00:33:51,810 --> 00:33:54,705
帕金斯先生，我沒說要賒帳
{\fs12}I didn't say nothing about no credit, Mr. Perkins.{\r}

313
00:33:54,825 --> 00:33:57,780
-你想訂購什麼？   -我需要一些麵粉...
{\fs12}-What you want to order?   -I need me some flour...{\r}

314
00:33:59,628 --> 00:34:01,096
肉荳蔻...
{\fs12}Nutmeg...{\r}

315
00:34:03,307 --> 00:34:04,794
巧克力...
{\fs12}Chocolate...{\r}

316
00:34:06,101 --> 00:34:07,895
[香草精] ...
{\fs12}Extract [of vanilla]...{\r}

317
00:34:08,015 --> 00:34:09,765
哦，還有一些糖...
{\fs12}Oh, and some sugar...{\r}

318
00:34:12,378 --> 00:34:14,047
並給我2個雞蛋
{\fs12}And give me 2 eggs.{\r}

319
00:34:14,911 --> 00:34:18,006
現在，我想和你談的是納森
{\fs12}Now what I want to talk to you about is Nathan.{\r}

320
00:34:18,126 --> 00:34:20,324
他不該做那件事
{\fs12}He oughtn't have done what he did.{\r}

321
00:34:20,968 --> 00:34:24,365
潛入傑米的地方，並拿走人家的貨物
{\fs12}Sneaking into Jamie's place and taking their goods.{\r}

322
00:34:25,149 --> 00:34:27,171
這對我來說很糟糕
{\fs12}That looks bad on me.{\r}

323
00:34:27,291 --> 00:34:29,322
我對你們都很好
{\fs12}I been good to y'all.{\r}

324
00:34:29,442 --> 00:34:32,160
我不是費盡苦心去說服蘭斯敦的人...
{\fs12}Didn't I go to all that trouble to get the people of Lansdowne...{\r}

325
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:36,017
...讓你的大衛李去唸他們的學校？不是嗎？
{\fs12}...to let your David Lee go to their school? Didn't I?{\r}

326
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,169
另一件事：
{\fs12}And another thing:{\r}

327
00:34:40,289 --> 00:34:42,742
納森進了監獄...
{\fs12}With Nathan in jail and all...{\r}

328
00:34:43,225 --> 00:34:47,758
...當春季到來時，你打算怎麼替我種地啊？
{\fs12}...how are you going to crop for me when the spring season comes? Huh?{\r}

329
00:34:49,125 --> 00:34:51,638
該死的，我在和你說話，女人！
{\fs12}Dammit, I'm talking to you, woman!{\r}

330
00:34:52,248 --> 00:34:55,746
我有一個農場要擔心，我需要一些回答
{\fs12}I've got a farm to worry about, and I need some answers.{\r}

331
00:34:57,816 --> 00:35:00,912
帕金斯先生，耕作季節還要很久才到
{\fs12}Cropping season is a long way off, Mr. Perkins.{\r}

332
00:35:01,032 --> 00:35:03,791
到那時，納森應該回家了
{\fs12}By that time, Nathan ought to be home.{\r}

333
00:35:03,911 --> 00:35:04,977
如果他不能...
{\fs12}If he ain't...{\r}

334
00:35:05,097 --> 00:35:07,791
...相信我，孩子和我會耕作
{\fs12}...believe me, the children and me will do the cropping.{\r}

335
00:35:07,911 --> 00:35:09,573
我們一定要的話
{\fs12}If we have too.{\r}

336
00:35:09,693 --> 00:35:12,367
因為我們還欠你錢
{\fs12}Because we owe you all that money.{\r}

337
00:35:12,769 --> 00:35:14,196
帕金斯先生
{\fs12}Mr. Perkins.{\r}

338
00:35:17,452 --> 00:35:19,422
你認為桑德死了嗎，大衛李？
{\fs12}Do you think Sounder's dead, David Lee?{\r}

339
00:35:19,542 --> 00:35:20,568
他會死嗎？
{\fs12}Will he stay dead?{\r}

340
00:35:20,688 --> 00:35:23,277
他沒死。別再問莫名其妙的問題
{\fs12}He ain't dead. Now stop asking crazy questions.{\r}

341
00:35:23,397 --> 00:35:25,811
你沒找到我們的死狗 也別生氣啊
{\fs12}You don't have to get mad because you didn't find our dead dog.{\r}

342
00:35:25,931 --> 00:35:27,243
他沒死！
{\fs12}He's not dead!{\r}

343
00:35:27,363 --> 00:35:28,328
大衛李？
{\fs12}David Lee?{\r}

344
00:35:28,448 --> 00:35:30,619
媽媽！媽媽，媽媽！
{\fs12}Mama! Mama, Mama!{\r}

345
00:35:30,739 --> 00:35:32,271
媽媽，媽媽！
{\fs12}Mama, Mama!{\r}

346
00:35:32,391 --> 00:35:33,557
主啊，好熱
{\fs12}Lord, it's hot.{\r}

347
00:35:33,677 --> 00:35:36,230
-有我的東西嗎？   -你們過得怎樣？
{\fs12}-Anything for me?   -How have y'all been?{\r}

348
00:35:36,350 --> 00:35:37,738
有人來過這裡嗎？
{\fs12}Anybody been here?{\r}

349
00:35:37,858 --> 00:35:40,800
-沒有，你看到爸了？    -沒有，兒子
{\fs12}-No, ma'am. You see Daddy? -No, son.{\r}

350
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:43,601
他必須等到假日到來
{\fs12}He'll have to wait until the holiday comes.{\r}

351
00:35:43,721 --> 00:35:47,279
無論如何，不准女人去探視自己的男人！
{\fs12}Anyway, won't let womenfolk see their men no time!{\r}

352
00:35:47,974 --> 00:35:51,934
-假日時我能去見他嗎？   -你肯定可以，兒子
{\fs12}-Can I see him when the holiday comes? -You sure can, son.{\r}

353
00:35:52,534 --> 00:35:54,322
有桑德的消息？
{\fs12}Any sign of Sounder?{\r}

354
00:35:54,442 --> 00:35:55,865
沒有，媽
{\fs12}No, ma'am.{\r}

355
00:35:55,985 --> 00:35:58,116
這些地方我都找遍了
{\fs12}I looked all over these parts.{\r}

356
00:35:58,236 --> 00:36:01,915
我想那一槍也許打中頭了
{\fs12}Well, I think maybe he was whipped on the head by that shot.{\r}

357
00:36:02,035 --> 00:36:03,865
我不認為他已經死了
{\fs12}I don't think he's dead.{\r}

358
00:36:03,985 --> 00:36:06,103
只是去某個地方 療養自己的傷
{\fs12}Just gone off to heal himself somewhere.{\r}

359
00:36:06,223 --> 00:36:07,633
這裡什麼都沒有
{\fs12}Nothing in here.{\r}

360
00:36:09,615 --> 00:36:10,741
沒有...
{\fs12}No...{\r}

361
00:36:10,861 --> 00:36:15,183
我正在做蛋糕，讓大衛李帶去給你爸爸
{\fs12}I'm fixing to bake a cake for David Lee to take to your daddy this time.{\r}

362
00:36:15,826 --> 00:36:17,803
做一個巧克力蛋糕，媽媽
{\fs12}Make a chocolate cake, Mama.{\r}

363
00:36:18,989 --> 00:36:21,743
爸爸喜歡有巧克力的東西
{\fs12}Daddy likes things that's chocolate.{\r}

364
00:36:25,092 --> 00:36:28,248
被告請起立，前進到法官席
{\fs12}Defendant will rise and come before the bench.{\r}

365
00:36:39,647 --> 00:36:41,516
納森李.摩根...
{\fs12}Nathan Lee Morgan...{\r}

366
00:36:41,636 --> 00:36:45,746
...你非法入侵，被判有罪...
{\fs12}...you have been found guilty of unlawful trespass..{\r}

367
00:36:45,866 --> 00:36:47,414
...還有搶劫
{\fs12}...and robbery.{\r}

368
00:36:48,338 --> 00:36:51,402
在法院宣判你的刑責之前，有什麼想對法庭說的嗎？
{\fs12}Is there anything you wish to say to the court, prior to...{\r}

369
00:36:51,412 --> 00:36:54,368
在法院宣判你的刑責之前，有什麼想對法庭說的嗎？
{\fs12}...the court pronouncing sentence upon you?{\r}

370
00:36:56,779 --> 00:36:57,884
沒有，先生
{\fs12}No, sir.{\r}

371
00:36:58,792 --> 00:37:02,701
本院判決，立即將你交付給本教區的警長收押...
{\fs12}The sentence of the court is that you be immediately remanded to the custody...{\r}

372
00:37:02,711 --> 00:37:04,667
本院判決，立即將你交付給本教區的警長收押...
{\fs12}...of the sheriff of this parish.{\r}

373
00:37:04,787 --> 00:37:09,970
未來將移送至指定的教區監獄營地，服勞役一年...
{\fs12}And that you be transferred forthwith to serve a term of 1 year at hard labor...{\r}

374
00:37:09,973 --> 00:37:14,121
未來將移送至指定的教區監獄營地，服勞役一年...
{\fs12}...at a parish prison camp to be hereafter designated.{\r}

375
00:37:14,830 --> 00:37:17,323
準備進行下一個案件
{\fs12}Collect and call the next case.{\r}

376
00:38:33,209 --> 00:38:34,757
桑德！
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

377
00:38:37,661 --> 00:38:39,189
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

378
00:38:47,943 --> 00:38:49,431
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

379
00:38:52,104 --> 00:38:53,652
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

380
00:38:56,078 --> 00:38:57,566
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

381
00:39:02,174 --> 00:39:03,682
{\fs12}Sounder!{\r}

382
00:39:25,756 --> 00:39:27,266
大衛李...
{\fs12}David Lee...{\r}

383
00:39:27,386 --> 00:39:30,871
一定要讓爸爸告訴你，他們要把他送到哪個營地
{\fs12}Be sure to ask your daddy to tell you what camp they're going to send him to.{\r}

384
00:39:30,991 --> 00:39:33,665
你現在看起來有點餓，所以一點也沒替他悲傷
{\fs12}Look perk-ish now, so you don't grieve him none.{\r}

385
00:39:33,785 --> 00:39:35,448
好吧，就這樣，兒子
{\fs12}OK, that's all, son.{\r}

386
00:39:36,255 --> 00:39:38,446
別忘記我告訴你的事，去吧！
{\fs12}Don't forget what I told you, now!{\r}

387
00:40:06,886 --> 00:40:08,937
你拿了什麼，男孩？
{\fs12}What have you got there, boy?{\r}

388
00:40:09,057 --> 00:40:10,363
給我爸的蛋糕
{\fs12}A cake for my daddy.{\r}

389
00:40:10,483 --> 00:40:13,961
放在這張桌子上，讓我先檢查
{\fs12}Well, put it on this table, and wait until I check it.{\r}

390
00:40:14,605 --> 00:40:16,764
男孩，再小心也不為過
{\fs12}Can't be too careful, boy.{\r}

391
00:40:16,884 --> 00:40:19,840
可能有銼刀或鋸子在裡面
{\fs12}There just might be a steel file or a hacksaw in it.{\r}

392
00:40:29,167 --> 00:40:30,856
你爸叫什麼名字？
{\fs12}What's your daddy's name?{\r}

393
00:40:30,976 --> 00:40:32,604
納森李.摩根
{\fs12}Nathan Lee Morgan.{\r}

394
00:40:35,794 --> 00:40:36,949
好的，男孩
{\fs12}OK, boy.{\r}

395
00:40:54,076 --> 00:40:56,549
你的右手邊，第三間牢房
{\fs12}3rd cell down there on your right.{\r}

396
00:41:07,615 --> 00:41:09,625
你來了。*
{\fs12}Well, look-y here.{\r}

397
00:41:11,423 --> 00:41:12,830
嗨，爸爸
{\fs12}Hi, Daddy.{\r}

398
00:41:13,152 --> 00:41:14,652
嗨
{\fs12}Hi back at you.{\r}

399
00:41:15,844 --> 00:41:18,557
媽媽和喬西梅和厄爾在外面
{\fs12}Mama's outside with Josie Mae and Earl.{\r}

400
00:41:22,256 --> 00:41:23,764
他們？
{\fs12}They is?{\r}

401
00:41:26,883 --> 00:41:28,370
呃...
{\fs12}Well...{\r}

402
00:41:29,395 --> 00:41:31,847
兒子，見到你好高興
{\fs12}It sure is good to see you, son.{\r}

403
00:41:33,033 --> 00:41:36,792
原本是個好蛋糕，被外面那個人戳的全是洞
{\fs12}This was a real cake, before the man outside put all these holes in it.{\r}

404
00:41:37,766 --> 00:41:40,721
哦，現在這沒多大差別
{\fs12}Oh, now, that don't make no difference.{\r}

405
00:41:42,510 --> 00:41:44,158
以我對你媽的認知...
{\fs12}If I know your mama...{\r}

406
00:41:44,278 --> 00:41:49,358
...一些刀孔不會破壞她在這塊蛋糕所下努心
{\fs12}...a few knife holes ain't gonna destroy the soul that she done put in this cake.{\r}

407
00:41:49,478 --> 00:41:52,473
給你，跟爸爸一起吃
{\fs12}Here. Now have a piece with your daddy.{\r}

408
00:41:57,666 --> 00:41:58,704
嗯...
{\fs12}Mmm...{\r}

409
00:41:59,958 --> 00:42:00,923
嗯
{\fs12}Mmm.{\r}

410
00:42:05,164 --> 00:42:06,222
爸爸...
{\fs12}Daddy...{\r}

411
00:42:06,342 --> 00:42:08,827
我們還沒有找到桑德
{\fs12}We didn't find Sounder yet.{\r}

412
00:42:08,947 --> 00:42:10,837
他有一天會露面
{\fs12}Well, he'll show up one day.{\r}

413
00:42:15,769 --> 00:42:17,477
他死了嗎，爸爸？
{\fs12}Think he's dead, Daddy?{\r}

414
00:42:18,321 --> 00:42:19,849
不，兒子
{\fs12}No, son.{\r}

415
00:42:20,191 --> 00:42:24,331
他的傷口一癒合就會立刻回你身邊，你等著看
{\fs12}He'll come back to you just as soon as his wounds heal. Now, you'll see.{\r}

416
00:42:24,451 --> 00:42:26,170
主啊...
{\fs12}Lord...{\r}

417
00:42:26,290 --> 00:42:28,320
...這個蛋糕真好吃
{\fs12}...this cake sure is tasty.{\r}

418
00:42:39,483 --> 00:42:42,458
很遺憾他們不會讓他們進來
{\fs12}It's a shame they won't let them come in here.{\r}

419
00:42:44,271 --> 00:42:48,834
如果我有力量，我會打倒這該死的牆壁，就可以...
{\fs12}Boy, if I had the strength, I'd knock down these damn walls just so I could...{\r}

420
00:42:48,954 --> 00:42:51,735
...去摟著你媽媽，只是...
{\fs12}...get my arms around your mama, just...{\r}

421
00:42:52,941 --> 00:42:55,193
你覺得他們會在我們這一邊嗎？
{\fs12}Are they on this side of us, do you think?{\r}

422
00:42:55,313 --> 00:42:56,761
應該是
