{\fs12}"...and it would be good for you to be here by the 4th or 5th of the month."{\r}

983
01:34:52,267 --> 01:34:55,613
“我希望一切都很好，你會在這裡。”
{\fs12}"I do hope everything is fine and you will be here."{\r}

984
01:34:55,733 --> 01:34:57,727
