等一下。你不告訴我你不會做什麼。我告訴你！
{\fs12}Wait just a minute. You don't tell me what you ain't gonna do. I tell you!{\r}

1009
01:36:11,096 --> 01:36:13,924
如果我說你要去那所學校就要去。現在來吧，我不...
{\fs12}And if I say you're going to that school you're going. Now come on, I don't...{\r}

